data.description: OPEN HOUSE SATURDAY Feb 3 12-2pm. Fall in LOVE with this Immaculate Napa Valley-inspired design with vaulted and WOOD-BEAMED CIELINGS, hardwood floors, SKYLIGHTS, a brick FIREPLACE and gorgeous copper lighting in the kitchen/breakfast room. One-story home great for entertaining, with an OPEN FLOOR PLAN connecting the living/dining and bar area to the kitchen, breakfast room, and lovely SUNROOM. Large Primary bedroom has double doors, natural light, WALK-IN CLOSET and bath offers DOUBLE SINKS, shower, and SPA TUB. LAUNDRY ROOM has a SINK, and a 1/2 bath is beyond the kitchen. PRIVATE YARD offers beautiful views with occasional deer stopping by. There's a NEW ROOF and a handy climate-controlled WORKSHOP/storage area in the back, plus an elegant iron fence with a gate leading to the front door-great for pets to enjoy the front garden area safely. The VIllage offers 26,000 Acres of Gated Security, with 11 Lakes and 9 Golf courses-this home sits right between Lake Balboa and Ponce de Leon Golf Course. Enjoy Pickleball, Tennis, a Fitness Center, miles of walking trails, and over 100 clubs! New Members are subject to a one time $1500 buy-in fee. See this GORGEOUS home TODAY!!
